CustomField.description: Used to flag "Dummy Assets" that are used in the "Work Done" process in case a field crew team member cannot find a Compkey or Serial number for an installed asset in their GIS application.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Please only tick this for "Dummy Assets" which should show up for field crew on the mobile app in the "Work Done" process in case they cannot find a CompKey in GIS.
CustomField.label: Is Dummy Asset
